node.text: If you’re looking for southwestern inspiration, @ryanditchphoto has got you covered with coverage. From the Sonoran desert to southern Utah to White Pocket - these otherworldly scenes and orange hues are brought to life with Ryan’s Alpha 7R V + 16-35mm F2.8 G Master I and II (which is the perfect set up for capturing wide landscapes in great detail, even after cropping in for socials.) 🏜️ #SonyAlpha
Hands down one of the best photographers to shoot the desert 😌
@jedstirr definitely adding it to the photo location bucket list 📝
Lots of amazing memories in Kanab! Such a cool town
These are fantastic, Ryne! I especially love that first shot.
